data.description: This home is a hybrid- partially manufactured double wide with added on rooms. It is located on a canal and has a dock and a seawall. The canaltakes you to Deer Point Lake. There is a large yard building/workshop located canal side and other covered storage area on the west side of the home. There isboth an open patio and covered porches. The living space is large and open to the kitchen. The bedrooms are all a decent size. The home is being sold strictlyAS-IS.
